                    textOnly="&lt;h3>IN THIS ARTICLE&lt;/h3>&#xd;&#xa;&lt;ul>&#xd;&#xa;&lt;li>&lt;span class=&quot;body-copy-large&quot;>AWE chooses the Shasta supercomputer for its ability to run mixed workloads and applications and workloads at the best TCO&lt;/span>&lt;/li>&#xd;&#xa;&lt;li>&lt;span class=&quot;body-copy-large&quot;>“Vulcan” will include the Slingshot interconnect, AMD processors, and ClusterStor storage&lt;/span>&lt;/li>&#xd;&#xa;&lt;/ul>&#xd;&#xa;"
                    topPadding="30"/>
                <horizontalgrayruleli
